cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.DS, cs.IT 

This paper deals with the statistical properties of human language, which is a topic of interest in computational linguistics (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses mathematical conjectures in coding theory (cs.CC) and discusses the operational definition of words, which is related to data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT).
